items.title: Zelenskyy says Putin 'definitely' not preparing to end war despite Trump summit
items.description: Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy claimed on Tuesday that Russian President Vladimir Putin is preparing for "new offensive operations."

items.title: Trump's remarks on homelessness in DC spark concerns among homeless advocates
items.description: President Donald Trump vowed this week to rid Washington, D.C., of homeless encampments, though what those plans will look like are unclear.
